title: Unable to import service design file
content:
The capsule installation fails andÂ you may come across the following error message:

Unable to import service design file 'SERVICE_OFFERING_Bulk_Import_Existing_Servers_-_Admin_Only_90cd933950d5f6380151243795f82a7a' with version '16.07.null'.

Possible causes

  • Cause 1: Any of the required OO content pack flows are missing in OO Central.
  • Cause 2: Content pack version in OO Central is incompatible with the DND version.

Solution

  • Check the Content Store logs.
  • Check if any flows are missing in any content packs in OO Central. If flow/flows are missing, update the content packs with the required flow/flows.
  • Check if the version of the content pack is compatible with the DND version. If the version is incompatible, then update the content pack version.
